# Write-allowlist for slackcli
#
# One Slack channel ID per line. The CLI will only send messages, add reactions,
# delete messages, forward, or upload snippets to channels listed here.
#
# Copy this file to allowlist.txt (gitignored) and add your channel IDs:
#
#   cp allowlist.txt.example allowlist.txt
#
# Find a channel's ID in Slack: open the channel → channel name dropdown →
# scroll to the bottom — the ID starts with C or G.
#
# Format:
#   CXXXXXXXXXX          bare channel ID
#   CXXXXXXXXXX  # note  inline comment is stripped
#   # full-line comment  ignored

# Example:
# C0123456789  # #general
# C9876543210  # #team-alerts
